CONMEBOL has announced the Copa America 2021 team of the tournament. The Copa America 2021 ended on Sunday morning with Argentina beating Brazil 1-0 in the final. Paris Saint-Germain’s Angel Di Maria scored the only goal of the match in the first half to give Argentina the victory against Brazil. Below is CONMEBOL’s Copa America 2021 team: Forwards: Diaz, Neymar and Messi. Midfielders: Yotun, Casemiro
and De Paul. Defenders: Estupinan, Marquinhos, Romero and Isla. Goalkeeper: Martinez